'''升G大調'''是基於G{{music|sharp}}的大調，由G{{music|sharp}}、A{{music|sharp}}、B{{music|sharp}}、C{{music|sharp}}、D{{music|sharp}}、E{{music|sharp}}、F{{music|doublesharp}}組成。其調號除了六個升號外具一個重升號，屬於理論調。

== 簡介 ==
=== 音階 ===
升G小調的音階為：
:<score vorbis="1" lang="lilypond">  {
\override Score.TimeSignature #'stencil = ##f
\relative c'' {
  \clef treble \key gis \major \time 7/4 gis4 ais bis cis dis eis fisis gis fisis eis dis cis bis ais gis2
} }
</score>

=== 應用 ===
[[File:G-sharp_major_example.png|right]]
[[File:G-sharp_major_example_2.png|right]]
升G大調常被寫作其[[異名同音|異名同音]]大調[[降A大調|降A大調]]。但在一些樂曲的臨時轉調部分則會應用到此調，如[[約翰·塞巴斯蒂安·巴赫|約翰·塞巴斯蒂安·巴赫]]在《[[平均律鍵盤曲集|平均律鍵盤曲集]]》第一卷第三首的《升C大調前奏曲與賦格，BWV 848》為較著名的例子（見右圖）；該卷第十八首《升G小調前奏曲與賦格，BWV 863》之前奏曲以升G大調的皮卡第三度結尾；另外亦有分析指第二卷第三首的《升C大調前奏曲與賦格，BWV 872》中全曲的多處，以及第四首的《升C小調前奏曲與賦格，BWV 873》中賦格接近[[尾聲|尾聲]]的部分皆有使用升G大調。<ref>{{cite web|title=Bach: Prelude and Fugue No.3 in C♯ major, BWV 872 Analysis|url=https://tonic-chord.com/bach-prelude-and-fugue-no-3-in-c%E2%99%AF-major-bwv-872-analysis/|work=Tonic Chord|date=2018-05-08|accessdate=2020-07-20|archive-date=2020-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200720073511/https://tonic-chord.com/bach-prelude-and-fugue-no-3-in-c%E2%99%AF-major-bwv-872-analysis/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Bach: Prelude and Fugue No.4 in C♯ minor, BWV 873 Analysis|url=https://tonic-chord.com/bach-prelude-and-fugue-no-4-in-c%E2%99%AF-minor-bwv-873-analysis/|work=Tonic Chord|date=2018-05-08|accessdate=2020-07-20|archive-date=2020-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200720053139/https://tonic-chord.com/bach-prelude-and-fugue-no-4-in-c%E2%99%AF-minor-bwv-873-analysis/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

此外，[[弗雷德里克·蕭邦|弗雷德里克·蕭邦]]的《[[练习曲_(肖邦)|練習曲，Op. 25]]》第六首、《[[升C小調夜曲Op._posth._(蕭邦)|C小調夜曲，Op. posth.]]》、《第二鋼琴協奏曲》第二樂章等作品，以及[[查爾斯-瓦倫丹·阿爾堪|查爾斯-瓦倫丹·阿爾堪]]的《鋼琴奏鳴曲》及《練習曲，Op. 39》第8首等作品，亦曾短暫轉到此調，或以此調作為結尾。<ref>{{cite web|last=Nicholas|first=Jeremy|title=The Complete Études|url=https://www.hyperion-records.co.uk/dc.asp?dc=D_CDH55380|work=Hyperion|year=2010|accessdate=2020-07-20|archive-date=2020-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200720053046/https://www.hyperion-records.co.uk/dc.asp?dc=D_CDH55380|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Beggerow|first=Alan|title=Alkan - Grande Sonate 'Les quatre âges', Opus 33|url=https://muswrite.blogspot.com/2017/07/alkan-grande-sonate-les-quatre-ages.html|work=Musical Musings|date=2017-07-22|accessdate=2020-07-20|archive-date=2020-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200720053657/https://muswrite.blogspot.com/2017/07/alkan-grande-sonate-les-quatre-ages.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Eddie|first=William Alexander|title=Charles Valentin Alkan|publisher=Routledge|year=2017|isbn=9781351572286}}</ref>

[[約翰·福爾茲|約翰·福爾茲]]的《世界安魂曲》的樂譜最後數頁則直接以升G大調記譜，其調號以C{{music|sharp}}在首、F{{music|doublesharp}}在末（如上方音階譜例的寫法）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.musicsalesclassical.com/composer/work/14652|title=A World Requiem (1921)|work=Wise Music Classical|accessdate=2020-07-20|archive-date=2018-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180727085309/http://www.musicsalesclassical.com/composer/work/14652|dead-url=no}}</ref>

